Print a list of values from the turtle library

Usage:
  turtle list [command]

Available Commands:
  categories  Print all categories from the turtle library
  keywords    Print all keywords from the turtle library
  names       Print all names from the turtle library

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for list

Global Flags:
  -i, --indent string   indent for JSON output
  -p, --prefix string   prefix for JSON output

Use "turtle list [command] --help" for more information about a command.
